site_name: Site of Janet Adegoke Lesiure Centre, 56
description: Redevelopment of the site by the erection of a part two and part seven storey building to provide a health centre (Class D1), retail (Class A1) and IT cafe (Class A1) on the ground floors; replacement social services facility (Class B1) and health care centre (D1) on the first floors; 179 residential units (Class C3) on the upper floors with underground car parking (116 spaces) and landscaping.
